well since in had been so long i decided it was time to update, so here it is.today i hung out with nicole and alana and even though it was a million degrees out we walked to the trolley center and dressed up in ponchos. good fun. then  we came home. very exciting huh? yea i thought it was too.
im not gonna go on "vacation" agian for a long time it just makes me feel alone. to me it seems everyones got something goign on and im liek err... im in connecticut. no good

so... i went to new york city today! it twas amazing. there are so  many things you can go do. anywho, i had fun going to china town adn what not except for the really gross fish markets that make you wanna run away becasue they smell so terrible.eww eww and when i was walking by some man started holding the fish and smelling it, it was the weirdest thing ive ever seen. then i went to a giant candy store where the stairs had candy in them. that was pretty spiffy. however, it was some of the most expensive candy ive ever seen. but o well thats new york for ya. all in all i had fun. 
 fish is smelly.

yea so last nite i was laying in bed getting ready to go to sleep when all of a sudden i was wide awake and had this overwhelming feeling that something bad was going on. so i got up and checked on my family and sat on the compuper for a while. once i got off the compuper i still couldnt sleep because i couldnt shake that feeling. finally once i did fall asleep and i had a really weird dream in which i was at a mob oriented raffle. i have no idea what that was all about.

ahhh... so ive been hanging out with family, you knwo cousins,aunts,uncle,ect. the whole shindig. its been ok, but i still miss all the buddys. yea so i cant wait to see you all.

see ya soon
<33

so yea.. here i am in conecticut not doing much. i could really be doing the same exact thing at home. but o well at least here i get to see my cousins and grandparents.i miss you all!! and i hope to see you all when i get home.
<33

so yesterday lily,gill,nicole, and alana all stayed the night at my house. it was good fun. we didnt really do much we just hung out. but it was enjoyable because im not gonna see then or anyone else for about a month,because im lame! I wish i could have gotten to see some other people before i left but what can ya do. well thats about all. ill miss you guys!!

so yesterday ian,alex,bridget,nicole, steve Q, and myself all went on the trolley to downtown. good fun i'd say. we walked around horton plaza and got lost several times.then when we got food from mc donalds and ian, bridget, and steve Q left us and alex nicole and i got stuck eating where it smelled really bad.but we also got to listen to nicole tell us about how stuff around us reminded her of a bunch of different places. like greece, italy ect. after that we got amazing soda that sprayed everywhere. im in love with it.haha. later we wondered over to a fountain and played in it until we were all soaked. then we got back on the trolley to go home.and nicole left lilys jacket on the trolley. no good.ahh but we made it to nicoles and we all went swimming, in our clothes.
the end.

ok so i havent updated in a while so let me cover what ive been up to...well bridget akasha and myself went a little bananas.first we went into the laundry mat and climbd into giant dryers and spun ourselves around. then we went over to round table and decided to put pepper on the table.they called the cops and yelled at us.no good. and then we went swimming and made crazy animal noises really really loudly.

hmm..friday i did nothing it was sooo fun.saturday i went to lilys then we all went drinking for gill's birthday with akasha,jessica,jenny,kelly,jon(boring name), dustin, nicole, lily, bridget,and gillian. it was fun except i smoked a lot and that was no good. then ysterday was a recooperation day at akashas. and then today i got hair dye and had akasha dye my hair. it was fun,and now were watching practical magic.busy weekend for me.

yesterday;friday,was good. after school lily,alex,ian, and i all hungout.we didnt really do much other then go down to hill creek and swing.o yes we also watched alex be mean to little kids. hee hee. today is gonna be fun! that's it

ok my step brothers wedding is over.yay! but it wouldnt have been complete unless my step mom yelled at me, o well.anywho after the wedding i went over to my friend lily's house where lily, nicole, and i all hung out. we decided to go to the beach and when we did about twenty 30 year old drunk men talked to us,eww. we went on the tilk a whirl and took a bunch of silly pistures(i would post them but i dunno how yet). so that was how i spent my saturday.

hmm... i went to school and i fell asleep in spanish, akasha came over after school, we worked on her power point, and now i am going to a stupid wedding rehersal. thats all.
